Johnny Depp is Off the Market! Actor Marries Amber Heard in Private Ceremony in Los Angeles Home

Just recently, Johnny Depp told E! News that he "couldn't wait" to marry Amber Heard... and apparently he wasn't kidding! Days before their scheduled wedding ceremony in the Bahamas, the couple made it official legally.
